<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Bug" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Bug,</orth> bugbear: <cit><quote>fear boys with --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.211" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 211</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the b. which you would fright me with,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.93" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 2, 93</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>Warwick was a b. that feared us all,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.2.2" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C V, 2, 2</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>such --s and goblins,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 2, 22</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>are grown the mortal --s o' the field,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 5.3.51" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 3, 51</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>